_sText:
Hi, I'm very happy to present you my first "map" (yes because it's a prefab).

So, I called this english_alphabet like I could call this french_alphabet etc... because I made the 26 letters in block of course, and in lasers.
I used different colors not for the beauty but for the difference between the letters and you can change the colors.
The size of these letters is 80x48 (except for the letter I).

If you have any questions, suggestions or something else to say, you can of course comment, I'll answer you.  

BobiNATRON.
